# Hotel Reservation System

This is a Java-based Hotel Reservation System developed for the CodeAlpha Java Programming Internship.

## Features

- View available hotel rooms
- Book hotel rooms
- Cancel room bookings
- View booking details
- Payment simulation
- Room categorization (Standard, Deluxe, Suite)

## Technologies Used

- Java
- OOP Concepts
- ArrayList
- Scanner Class

## Project Structure

- Room Management
- Booking Management
- Reservation Cancellation
- Console-Based Interface

## How to Run

1. Open project in IntelliJ IDEA or Eclipse
2. Compile the Java file
3. Run `HotelReservationSystem.java`

